column5: SO if the weather is good im going out at 0530 consider this an invitation for 1 person you dont need gear just bring your own whatever not looking for anyone to split costs just an offer to fish probably be back in by 0930 depending on the bite kings seem to be on with decent sizes and rainbows are on as well it would be good if you had a boaters card because you can drive while I set up when i say im leaving at 0530 I am first person thta pms me and is serious your good to go  Peter  This is where the launch is
Nice guy   I would love to go but unfortunately I can't.  Bump it up!
If this was for Saturday I would be in
I wish I caught this yesterday, would have been there...
